Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.30,0:00:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同志们 这是我办过最棒的一次洗衣派对了\NGuys,this is the best laundry party I've ever thrown.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.82,0:00:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是所有词后面加上"派对" 都能变得很欢乐\NYou can't just stick the word "party" on anything and make it fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.60,0:00:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不爽是因为错过了Brad的牙龈手术派对\NYou're just mad because you missed Brad's gum surgery party.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.11,0:00:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下周我要去颗痣 留点时间\NWell,save the date,because next week... I'm having an asymmetrical mole removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.02,0:00:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,派对主题是"康复凯旋"\NThe theme will either be "dressed to the benigns"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者"安排后事"\Nor "it's time to get my affairs in order."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要洗的衣服还真不少\NOoh! That's a lot of laundry,buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这都是要来的\NActually,this is all candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一路玩着"不给就捣乱"过来的\NYeah. I trick-or-treated my way over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离万圣节还早着呢\NIt's not even close to Halloween.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.11,0:00:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可事实证明只要按别人家门铃\NYeah,but it turns out if you ring someone's doorbell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.11,0:00:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冲着他们使劲吼"不给就捣乱"\Nand then scream in their face "trick or treat?" as loud as you can,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.52,0:00:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要什么他们都给你\Nthey'll just give you whatever they have on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.34,0:00:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙把他要洗的衣服都塞给我了\NThis one guy-- he gave me all his laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.49,0:00:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最棒的是全都是特大号的\NAnd the cool is that it's all XXL,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.80,0:00:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我再胖点还能穿\Nso I have room to grow into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.38,0:00:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个奇葩\NYou're a terrifying individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.97,0:00:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dave 衬衣要跟我的一起洗吗\NOh,hey,Dave,you wanna throw your shirts in with mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.01,0:00:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不 我这几件需要特殊对待\NOh,no,no,no. These-- these require special attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都穿在身上跑动晾干\NIn fact,sometimes I throw them on wet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.69,0:00:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好让衣服不变形\Nand run-dry them so they keep their shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我出了一身汗 又得重新洗\NBut then I get all sweaty,and it's like,here we go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样 要做自己\NWould not change a thing about what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.25,0:00:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谢谢你 - 老天\N- Thank you. - Oh,my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:01:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水族馆有个团购 跟海豚游泳\NThere's a groupon at the aquarium to swim with the dolphins.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.46,0:01:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 老娘超爱海豚 - 别\N- Mama likes dolphins. - Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.89,0:01:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你总这样\NMama always does this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.52,0:01:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看见喜欢的就买 转身就没兴趣了\NYou see something you like,you buy it, and then you lose interest immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你太冲动了 - 我才没有冲动\N- You're too impulsive. - I am not too impulsive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在坦帕订了限时度假屋\NYou bought us a time-share in Tampa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中介说那是东部的萨克拉门托\NThe lady at the kiosk said it's the Sacramento of the East.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.90,0:01:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在每年都要去坦帕了\NNow we gotta go to Tampa every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.85,0:01:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去Tampa不是旅游 是养老\NTampa's not a place that you go. It's a place that you end up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.58,0:01:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我家这位也这样 - 咋啦\N- My bitch is the same way. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.24,0:01:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brad在购物台买了好多垃圾 我们自己都能开个节目卖了\NBrad buys so much junk on QVC,we could start our own show.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.39,0:01:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过不行\NBut we won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管你说什么 Jane 那可不是垃圾\NWhatever,Jane. It's not junk, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.57,0:01:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如 你们这些小猪洗衣服的时候\NFor example,while you porkers have been doing laundry,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.23,0:01:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我却坐在这里 锻炼腹肌\NI've been sitting here,getting a killer ab workout
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.41,0:01:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用我新买的腹肌带\Nwith my new... electro ab-belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在电动脉冲刺激下...\NThe electro-pulse stimulation...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.15,0:01:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重塑你的...腹肌!\NTones and shapes your ...abs!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给塑形新的...定义!\NFor improved muscle defi...nition!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.10,0:01:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来...\NAnyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.85,0:01:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我预测Alex团购了也不会用\NI predict that Alex buys the groupon and never uses it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.79,0:01:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对会用的\NI am absolutely gonna use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.23,0:01:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 你囤了多少团购券\NOkay,how many unredeemed groupons do you have currently?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.49,0:02:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.87,0:02:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 多少 - 11个\N- How many? - 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.19,0:02:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,11个 我觉得你该吸取教训了\N11. Okay. Well,I think it's time that you learned a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样吧 如果你一周内用完所有团购券\NTell you what. If you use all your groupons in one week,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.62,0:02:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就送你海豚的团购 还跟你一起去\NI'll buy you that dolphin groupon and... I'll do it with ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.13,0:02:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一言为定\NYou're on,ping-pong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.93,0:02:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\NMm. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好运 Alex 我支...持你\NWell good luck,Alex. I'm rooting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.93,0:02:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗\NOkay? You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.16,0:02:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想说的是\NWhat I meant to say is,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我挺...你!\NI'm in your...corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天哪\NOh,God!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它...不停顿了\NIt's just-- it's not even pulsing anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 快脱下来 - 一直电击\N- Get that off of him. - It's just constant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.47,0:02:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 痛死我了! - 电到我了!\N- So painful! - It shocked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 弄下来! - 我在弄 开关在哪\N- Take it off! - All right. I'm trying. I don't know where the--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.93,0:02:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得垫个垃圾袋坐\NI need to sit on a trash bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 垃圾袋 需要... - 别\N- We need a trash bag. We just-- it happened. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,常有的事 没关系\NIt's happens. It just happens. It's okay. It's okay.
