Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<font color=#70DB93>幸福终点站 第3季 第21集</font>\N<font color=#70DB93>Happy.Endings S3Ep21</font>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次我把仿麂皮外套落在那了\NLast time I was there,I think I left a suede jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.29,0:02:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想找回来 不管猫还在不在里面\NI'd love to get that back,with or without the cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我在衣服里养了只猫\NOh,PS. There's a live cat living in that jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.06,0:02:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天哪\NOh,my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:03:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看见那个被我毁一生 所以要毁我一生的男人\NI see the guy whose life I ruined, who in turn vowed to ruin mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是找到我的外套猫 叫它外套猫\NIf you find my coat cat,he answers to the name "coat cat."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要挂了 拜!\NGotta go. Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 Chase\NHey,Chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥们 知道什么最酷吗\NBuddy,old pal. You know what's cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次我们见面时 一切都好的不能再好了\NThe last time we saw each other, we left things on the best terms possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在找你 Max\NI've been looking for you,Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要告诉我你重获工作 又和妻子复合了吗\NTo tell me that you're back at work and that you're back with your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 多亏你 我现在还没工作\NNope. Thanks to you,I'm still unemployed,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我前妻跟我弟弟订婚了\Nand my ex-wife's engaged to my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想自杀 不过你猜 谁要在他们婚礼上祝酒\NI'd kill myself, but guess who has to give a toast at their wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天 还真是祸不单行\NOoh,boy. That is rough'em stuff'em robots,pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.76,0:03:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟踪你好几周了 想着搞个计划毁掉你的人生\NI've been following you for weeks, trying to craft a plan to ruin your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.28,0:03:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好笑的是 你的人生已经绝顶悲催了\NFunny thing is,your life is so pathetic I doubt I can make it any worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,破坏不能\NIt's un-sabotagable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这样嘛 最近我日子过的挺好的\NHey. Come on. I got a lot of stuff going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我刚买了长柄勺 盛汤用\NI,uh,recently bought a ladle... for soups.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我读了半篇关于鱼肝油的报道\NI,uh,I read half an article on fish oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我刚学会海姆利克急救法\NAnd,uh,I just learned how to do the heimlich.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对自己也行 再也不用担心嚼东西了\NCan even do it on myself,so now chewing food is my prerogative.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的人生太渣了\NYour life sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有工作 没有爱情 公寓乱七八糟\NYou have no job,no love life. Your apartment is disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.54,0:03:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想过放老鼠进去\NI considered releasing rats in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.89,0:04:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你家里的老鼠比我的还大\Nbut you already had rats in there way bigger than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.89,0:04:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别自责 兄弟\NDon't beat yourself up,pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都尽力养自己的鼠\NWe're all just raising our rats the best we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你 我不想再毁你人生了\NWhat I'm trying to say is,I'm not gonna ruin your life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为已经糟到无可复加了\Nbecause it's impossible to ruin something that's already terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就好比在人人加了好几个妈做好友\NIt'd be like adding more moms to Facebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Penny 花钱请洁耳工去你家\NPenny,aren't you sick of paying a professional ear cleaner
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你痛苦的去除耳垢 你就不烦吗\Nto come to your house and painfully remove your unwanted canal wax?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brad 我知道Jane让你把那些玩意都卖掉\NLook,Brad,I know Jane's making you sell all your little gadgets,but--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不用麻烦了 只要有了...新型洁耳机\NWell,now you don't have to... with the revolutionary ear genie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 试试吧 - 不要! 什么\N- Try it out. - No! What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.80,0:04:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要买你用过的洁耳机\NNo,I do not wanna buy your used ear cleaner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全理解 我懂的\NTotally understand. I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来聊聊鞋子吧 你都怎么加热的\NLet's talk shoes. How are you heating yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有麻烦了 我要帮助\NI have a problem! I need help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有麻烦了 我要帮助\NI have a problem and I need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不 我先 - 好了 好了\N- No! Me! - Okay,okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alex先说\NAlex first. Alex first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.87,0:04:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 谢啦\NOkay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道Dave约定用完团购券的事吧\NSo you know how Dave challenged me to do all these groupons?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直不在状态\NI-I keep getting distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今早的陶艺课就没去\NI didn't even make it to my pottery class this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}小狗派对\N{\a6}It's a... puppy party!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:05:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好多的小狗狗啊\NIt was a total puppy pile-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你没用团购券\NSo you never used your pottery groupon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 说明你还有11个 - 12个\N- Which means you still have 11. - 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宠物店的人说有增长睫毛的团购\NThe puppy store lady said that there was a groupon for eyelash extensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很需要 我睫毛像我爸 又短又粗\NI need those! I have my dad's stubby eyelashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们要陪我一起 让我抓紧用完\NYou guys have to do these groupons with me, keep me on track.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为请求救援专家\NWell,as the author of several dozen cries for help,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久病成医 我知道什么请求可以救\NI know a good one when I hear one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.22,0:05:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是公平起见\NBut we have to be fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.58,0:05:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了公民的利益\NIn the interest of conducting a civil discourse,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊利诺伊州的肥仔也聊一聊吧\Nthe fat slob from Illinois has the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 你们记得Chase吧\NThank you. Now you guys remember Chase,right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 记得 人超酷 发誓要毁你人生 - 就是他\N- Yes. Super cool guy,vowed to ruin your life.- That's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说我的人生已经糟到极点 破坏不能\NWell,he said that my life is so pathetic that it is un-sabotagable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要改善生活 证明他是错的\NSo I need to improve my life to prove him wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个 Max...\NWell,Max...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们喜欢挑战\Nyou know we love a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是自杀行径不属于挑战范畴\NBut that's not so much a challenge as it is a suicide mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们选择帮Alex - 太棒了!\N- So we're gonna go with Alex! - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 你自己看着办吧\NSorry,brah. You're on your ahn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是大兵瑞恩 我也不跟Tom Hanks握手\NYou ain't Private Ryan, and I ain't shaking hands with Tom Hanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Max 只有一个人喜欢这个挑战\NMax,there's only one person who's really up to this challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:06:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我等你来等了10年了\NI've waited ten years for you to come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你从哪找到我穿内裤的照片\NHow did you get a picture of me in my underwear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都只穿内裤的啊\NWell,you're-- you're always in your underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很难找到一张你穿衣服的\NIn fact,it's hard to find a picture of you when you're clothed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要挑战的任务艰巨难当\NI do not envy the task you are about to embark on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.83,0:06:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,红箭头是干什么用的\NWhat are all those red arrows for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是你要改善的部位\NOh,those are all the areas that need improvements.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是全部了\NBut those are all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你失败的地方挺多的\NYeah. You got lots of bad areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是同性恋的下限\NYou're like the Oakland of gay guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 从哪开始\NOkay. Well,where do we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,细节 比如头发 淋浴\NSmall stuff-- haircut,shower,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别再问服务员菜能不能做成千层面\Nstop asking waiters if your food could be "lasagna'd."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jane 用你的强迫症拯救我吧\NJane,I'm in your undiagnosed OCD hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们开始吧\NLet's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞧瞧谁在这\NWell,well,well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是怀疑的Dave么\Nif it isn't doubting Dave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能要叫怀疑的海豚人Dave了\NMight have to start calling you "doubting dolphin Dave."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用掉了几张团购券很爽吧\NFeeling pretty good 'cause you knocked out a few groupons,huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不止几张 是很多张\NNot just a few. Many few.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们买了带帽围巾\NWe got these cool hooded scarves...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还洁了两次牙\Nand we got our teeth whitened... twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洁牙哦\NWhitened up them teeth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们还去画像了 给他看\NAnd we took this gorgeous portrait. Show him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.67,0:07:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 是不是很美\NGot it. Isn't it beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像两个拉拉领养了个苏丹失足少年\NIt's like a portrait of two lipstick lesbians who adopted a lost boy of Sudan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 很开心\NYeah,it's just been good times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 龙舌兰\NOh! You guys,up next... tequila shots!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.86,0:08:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,团购...半价\N50% off... with this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\NSi,senor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我恨龙舌兰\NI hate tequila.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,团购太惨无人道了\NThese groupons are the worst thing ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.41,0:08:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最糟的是以这速度\NNo,the worst thing ever is that at this rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alex明天就能用完这些券\NAlex is gonna finish these groupons by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.49,0:08:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道该怎么办么\NYou know what we need to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.94,0:08:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们该捣乱 让她完不成\NWe need to sabotage her so she can't finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么\NWhy would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为如果Alex赢了\NBecause,Pen,if Alex wins this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她会拉你团购一辈子的\Nshe's gonna be dragging you to groupons for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你希望50岁还单身一人 去半价的高空杂技课么\NYou wanna be 50 years old and single and doing half-priced trapeze lessons?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不爽你假设我还单身\NI resent you making me single in this hypothetical.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少让我有尊严的守寡\NSee,you could've at least given me the dignity of having been widowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干杯\NOkay! Down the hatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们修眉团购10分钟后开始\NOur brow-shaping groupon is in 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要在眼睛间打激光\NThey shoot a laser right between your eyeballs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 准备好了么 - 嗯\N- Here. Ready,Pen?! - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 咱们整垮这贱人吧 - 好\N- Let's take that bitch down. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jane\NJane!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来看这机器 太棒了\NCheck out this machine. It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它能从地面吸走垃圾\NIt sucks the garbage off the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:08:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我不用破兜装垃圾\Nso now I don't have to throw it out on the street
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好偷着扔到马路上了\Nthrough a hole in my pocket,Andy Dufresne style.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Max 你看上去很棒\NMax,you look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.03,0:09:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很棒\NI mean,really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉很好\NI feel great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上我洁牙时牙龈只流了很多血\NThis morning,I flossed my mouth, and my gums only bled a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是非常多的血\Nas opposed to an alarming amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天去商店面试了吧\NAnd you had that interview today at that grocery store?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进展怎样\NHow did that go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.85,0:09:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完胜\NI nailed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超市最糟了\NThis supermarket is the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你该这么做\NHere's what you gotta do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把甜麦片从底层移到顶层\NYou gotta move the sugar cereals from the bottom shelf to the top shelf,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我这种人不会或不能弯腰去拿\N'cause people like me don't and/or can't bend over to pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是应征装袋工的么\NI thought you were here for the bagger position?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说了 有问题么 快说\NI said,any questions?! Chop-chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.99,0:09:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说完胜么\NI thought you said you nailed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实完胜啊\NI did nail it,Jane.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事实上...他们让我做...\NIn fact... they're making me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,经理助理\Nassistant manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.79,0:09:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能\NNo way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小菜一碟\NCurds and whey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.82,0:09:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说喜欢我的实话和新观点\NGuy said he liked my real talk and fresh takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.94,0:09:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,计划比想象中进展快的多啊\NWow. My plan is working much faster than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔细想想…\NCome to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.51,0:09:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是太快了\Nmaybe a little too fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然很开心 乳头都不疼了\NI mean,I'm weirdly happy. My nipples stopped burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前没人喜欢我的实话和新想法\NNo one likes my real talk and fresh takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:09:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个人喜欢\NOnce,a guy liked my real fresh take on talks,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那人是我 我是骗人的\Nand that guy was me,and I was lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想说什么\NWhat is your point?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仅凭我自己没可能改变这么大\NThere's no way my life could've turned around this quickly on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一解释是Chase在偷偷改善我的生活\NThe only logical explanation is that Chase is secretly trying to improve it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捧高摔重\Nbuilding me up only to knock me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你疯了吧\NThat is crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放松 享受过程\NJust relax and enjoy your progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,享受过程 是么\NEnjoy the progress,huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Chase也会这么说 - 什么\N- That's exactly what Chase would say! - What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现身吧\NShow yourself,you beautiful genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Max - 让我撕碎这张皮\N- Max! - I'll tear this face off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够了\NAll righty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Max 我不是Chase\NMax,I'm not Chase!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我错了\NMy bad,Jane.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 实话说 - 嗯\N- Full disclosh, though? - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是第一次觉得你是汉子了\NNot the first time I thought you were a dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.39,0:10:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.43,0:10:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是Alex海豚团购的最后期限\NOkay. Today is the last day that Alex's dolphin groupon is available.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们要让她不能用完剩下的券 - 对\N- All we have to do is make sure she doesn't finish the others.- Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你 Alex和Brad\NSo you,Alex,and Brad are supposed to go to dinner tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去新的烧烤店晚餐\Nat that new barbecue joint,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是不用去了 因为我俩要\Nexcept you're not because you and I are gonna--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用手机砸窗户\NThrow the phones through the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让菜盘里全是碎玻璃和手机\Ncovering their pulled pork with shattered glass and phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:11:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么 我们要打电话定很多位\NWhat? No. No,we're gonna call and make so many reservations
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你们去不成\Nthat you guys can't get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了很重要的一点\NBut you are overlooking one very obvious detail--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,餐馆会记下我们电话号的\Nthe restaurant is gonna recognize our number.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我弄了这些一次性的\NThat's why I got all these burners,baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.28,0:11:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来砸订餐员 干扰他\NTo throw at the reservation guy to distract him. Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不不 蠢货\NNo! No! You fool,no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们从40个不同的身份和手机打电话\NWe call from 40 different phones using 40 different personas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的\NHere are yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南方律师\NUh,Southern lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"我确认"\N"I do declare."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,楠塔基特岛家庭主妇\NNantucket housewife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"来杯白葡萄酒"\N"Uh,white wine spritzer,please?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Julian Assange 维基泄密那家伙么\NJulian Assange? Is that the Wikileaks guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我演不了他 - 要我演他么\N- I can't do him. - You want me to do him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随便 把握角色的精髓\NWhatever. Just honor the spirit of the characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也要好好玩哦\NBut don't forget to have fun out there,okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的第一个角色是Alex\NNow your first character is Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以她名义打电话给餐厅 取消订位\NCall the restaurant as her and cancel the reservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.32,0:11:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不知道能不能行 - 你可以的\N- Oh,I don't know if I can do this. - You got this. You got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是Alex Kerkovich\NHey,I'm Alex Kerkovich.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很矮而且我喜欢排骨\NI'm short and I love ribs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你了解Alex和订位流程么\NDo you know anything about Alex or how reservations work?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.01,0:11:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她听起来就这样\NThis is what she sounds like!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要取消预订\NI need to cancel a reservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 谢谢\Nfantastic. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惨了\NWe're screwed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:12:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她已经去了 而且把三张排骨团购都用了\NShe has been there already and used all three ribs groupons herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.88,0:12:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了排骨是她早餐最爱\NGod,we should've known. Breakfast ribs are her favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完了完了完了\NDamn,damn,damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛这么急 不过一个赌而已\NWait. Why do you care so much? I... it's just a bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我关心Alex\NBecause I care about Alex,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要让她成熟点 负责任地用钱\Nand I'm trying to help her grow up and be more responsible with her money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.26,0:12:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正原因是什么\NWhat's the real reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.45,0:12:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对海豚有种偏执的恐惧\NI have a paralyzing fear of dolphins--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一接近它们\Nas in,when I'm near them...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就大便失禁\NI lose my poop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 现在只剩一张团购券了\NNow come on. There's only one groupon left,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在健身营的军事障碍课\Nand it's the military obstacle course at the Major Fitness Boot Camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果她用了 我就输了\NIf she does this,I lose,all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 所以我们必须阻止她 - 好\N- So we gotta stop her. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么怕海豚 它们那么无害\NWhy dolphins? They seem so sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们懂的很多\NLet's just say they understand a lot of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但偏偏不懂“不”的意思\Nbut "no" isn't one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Max\NHey, Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 新工作怎样 - 很好\N- How's the new job? - Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了\NActually,too great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我信用卡今早申到了 牙也不疼了\NThis morning,I got approved for a credit card, my teeth stopped burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chase肯定做了什么\NThere's no way Chase is not behind all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这都是每天发生的平常事\NMax,that is just normal stuff that happens to pretty much everyone every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天 她噎着了\NOh,my God. She's choking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kevin 该怎么办\NKevin! I don't know what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么都非我不可么\NDo I have to do everything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了么 来了\NOkay,ready? Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heimlich急救法 数到三 一 二 三\NHeimlich on three. One,two,three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 太好了 - 不好\N- It's great! - No,it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chase知道我在学急救术\NChase knows that I've been learning CPR.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是这一切的幕后推手\NHe is behind everything that's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这只是个巧合\NIt's a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢\NThank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是芝加哥WLS的记者\NI'm a reporter for WLS Chicago,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要让我做个关于你的报道\Nand you've gotta let me do a story about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是个真正的英雄\NYou're a real hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗯 一定是Chase - 对 是Chase\N- Yeah,it's Chase. - Yeah,it's Chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到少校健身训练营\NWelcome to the Major Fitness Boot Camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有一张军事障碍课的团购券\NWe have a groupon to use the military obstacle course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迫不及待啊 上吧\NYep. Can't wait. Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.08,0:13:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 这儿关闭了\NSorry,it's closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,场地被水淹了 极其恶心 女士\NThe course is flooded. It's super yucky,ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那我们要克服的障碍就只剩失望了\NWelp,I guess the only obstacle left for us to overcome is disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样了? 我输了?\NThat's it? I lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\NI'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么话都非要用吼的么\NDo you have to yell everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:13:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吼是因为受了伤\NI'm yelling on account of my injury!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得 在战斗中听力受损\NOf course. You lost your hearing in combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你为维护自由做出的牺牲\NWell,we appreciate the sacrifice you've made to preserve our freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.10,0:14:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我用了电视购物的洁耳机 把耳膜弄破了\NI busted my eardrums using that ear genie ear wax remover you buy on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别用玩意儿\NStay away from them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦\NWell,well,well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Penny说你没完成障碍课程\NPenny told me you didn't finish the obstacle course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来跟海豚在水族缸游泳的时间\NSo it looks like instead of swimming in a tank with dolphins,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.73,0:14:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只好用来泡在咱的浴缸里 读那本没劲的"时间旅行者的妻子"了\NI'll be soaking in our tub with a well-worn copy of "The Time Traveler's Wife."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 你赢了 我输了\NYeah,you won. I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说得对 我总是做错误的决定\NYou're right. I make terrible decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是个冲动的傻瓜\NI'm an impulsive idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦 我觉得不至于是傻瓜\NOh,honey,come on. I wouldn't say "idiot."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的? 我回家路上买的这台棉花糖机\NReally? The cotton candy maker I bought on the way home
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能不同意这点\Nmight disagree with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.34,0:14:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它不能说话 那种要贵200刀\NIt doesn't actually talk. Those were,like,$200 more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别太苛求自己了\NHey,listen. Don't beat yourself up over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜欢棉花糖\NI love cotton candy,too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我准备把它退了\NWell,I am returning it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.53,0:14:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我该拨开迷云\N'cause it's time for me to get my head out of the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:15:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不能吃像云一样的东西了\Nand stop eating food that looks like clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花椰菜就挺健康 也像云朵啊\NCauliflower is healthy,and it looks like clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.30,0:15:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下我糊涂了 而且饿了\NNow I'm confused... and hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不想来点美味蓬松的棉花糖?\NWould you care for some delicious, fluffy cotton candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我撒谎了 我多花了200刀\NI lied. I did spend the extra $200.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实际是300刀\NAnd it was... $300.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.03,0:15:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chase做得太漂亮了\NChase is doing some dang old good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向他脱帽致敬\NA tip of the ol' James hat to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不会让他享受摧毁我的快感的\NBut I am not gonna give him the satisfaction of destroying my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.77,0:15:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行\NNo,sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.56,0:15:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会自己来\NI'm gonna do that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你确定要这么做? - 嗯\N- You're sure you wanna do this? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令我心碎 不过没问题\NBreaks my heart,but okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.16,0:15:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是有全职工作的吧\NYou do have a full-time job,right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 就这样\NThere we go. Get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你差不多打回原形了\NWell,you're pretty much right back to where you started--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烟熏人肉\Nhuman pastrami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.92,0:16:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不够 Jane\NIt's not good enough,Jane.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得把我整到负五级\NYou gotta take me to negative 5,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确保Chase永远放过我\Nmake sure Chase stays away for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但再没什么好毁的了\NBut there's nothing left to destroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只剩健康了\NI mean,all you really have left is your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.88,0:16:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 这也拿去吧 揍我\NOkay. Take it. Hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不会揍你的\NNo,I'm not gonna hit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jane 你的脚踝好胖\NJane,you ankles are fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会中招呢\NYeah. I'm not falling for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jane 你的戚风蛋糕湿度不对\NJane,your bundt cake is on the wrong side of moist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡扯\NThat is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.37,0:16:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时你毫无准备 真是可悲啊\NAt times,you're woefully unprepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.97,0:16:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我第一次被个女人吸引\NThis is the first time I've ever been attracted to a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想让你怀上我的孩子\NI wanna put a baby in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.64,0:16:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们干嘛 带我来幸灾乐祸的么\NSo what'd you guys do,bring me here to gloat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:17:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alex 我要坦白一下\NAlex... I have a confession to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和Penny来了一出法式破坏艺术\NPenny and I engaged in the French art of sabotage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们淹了场地让你上不了课 - 什么\N- We flooded the course so you couldn't do it. - What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.39,0:17:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信\NI can't believe you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想眼睛被激光扫\NI didn't want a laser shot at my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这点无可厚非\NI don't think that's an unreasonable position.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我看见你和棉花糖机\NBut then,Alex,I saw you with that cotton candy machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我发现 我喜欢你的冲动和意气用事\Nand I realized that I love that you're impulsive and you do those kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的特质\NThat's what makes you,you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\NAw! Yeah,it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.59,0:17:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 我们真互补\NIt's great. We really complement each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是冲动的那个\NI mean,you're the impulsive one,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是踏实的那个 思路清楚\Nand I'm the grounded one that thinks things through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不不不 - 你才不踏实\N- No. No. No,no,no,no. - You're not grounded in the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 不\NNo. No. No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 超冲动 - 对\N- Super impulsive. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么就冲动了?\NHow am I impulsive?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看了"慕尼黑" 就想办犹太成人礼\NWhen you saw "Munich," you tried to get Bar Mitzvah'd.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.21,0:17:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在Alex的坦帕分时度假房隔壁 你又买了一套\NYou bought a time-share in Tampa next to Alex's.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.21,0:17:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你买了40个一次性手机来 做40个匿名晚餐预约\NYou bought 40 burner cell phones to make 40 untraceable dinner reservations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.27,0:17:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有脸上那堆胡子\NYou have the facial hair you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了我承认啦\NOkay,I get it! I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别怪到山羊胡头上就是\NLeave the goatee out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 很难做到 - 真的很难\N- It's hard to leave it out. - Really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还别说 也许俩冲动货也能美满在一起\NYou know what? Maybe two impulsive people can work in a relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.58,0:17:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌手Ice和Coco T就行\NHey,it works for Ice and Coco T.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确是呢\NSure as hell does.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是海豚团购券\NHere's the dolphin groupon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 给你之前 你得先完成障碍课程\NBut before I give it to you, you have to do the obstacle course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:17:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这里关闭了啊\NBut it's closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们冲动一回吧\NSo let's be impulsive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许一对冲动货也有不好的一面\NPerhaps there's a downside to having two impulsive people in a relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该提醒一下Ice和Coco T\NSomeone should warn Ice and Coco T.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你俩不能没人看着\NI don't think you guys should be left alone without supervision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就好像我们是俩30岁二货的父母\NYeah,it's like all of a sudden we're parents to two 30-year-old dum-dums.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三个\NThree.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Max 再次跟你说对不起\NMax,again,I am so,so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事 你干得好\NIt's okay. You did good,baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.02,0:18:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chase不能再伤害我们了\NChase can't hurt us anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.02,0:19:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Max是你么\NMax,is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chase 你怎么在这儿\NChase? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在路上谈过后\NAfter we spoke on the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.63,0:19:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我踩在你扔的一块披萨上滑倒了 还撞到了头\NI slipped on that slice of pizza you dropped and I hit my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.78,0:19:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都昏迷三天了\NI've been unconscious for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昏迷?\NUnconscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么不可能是你逆转我的生活 以求击溃我了\NSo then it couldn't have been you building my life up only to knock it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先 我还好 多谢关心\NFirst of all,I'm fine. Thanks for asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我没问 - 其次 不 我没有\N- I didn't ask. - Secondly,no,I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这儿正好 我想跟你说点事\NBut I'm so glad you're here because I wanna tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.86,0:19:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你死后会去哪\NI don't know where you fall in the existence of an afterlife,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.65,0:19:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我告诉你 还有另一个地方\Nbut I'm here to tell you there is another place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.45,0:19:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是一片性灵之境 主宰者强大而仁慈\NIt's a spiritual realm ruled by powerful yet merciful beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到过那里 Max\NI was there,Max,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.49,0:19:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迈向美好永恒的宁静\Nand I was headed for sweet eternal peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可我想起来\NBut then I realized
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还不能飞越到更高一层\NI could not transcend to the next plane
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非先把此世未竟之事了结\Nuntil I took care of the unfinished business of this world--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.46,0:19:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是摧毁你的生活\Nthe unfinished business of ruining your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是你\NIt was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.64,0:19:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会回来找你的\NI came back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.16,0:19:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我仔细俯瞰了彼岸世界的深渊\NI have looked deep into the abyss of the next world,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:20:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那十分美丽\Nand it is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但开始朝圣之旅前\NBut before I make that pilgrimage,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.73,0:20:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不会放弃破坏\NI will stop at nothing to lay waste
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可悲的所谓生活\Nto what you so tragically call your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他还是那么酷\NThat guy is still so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.14,0:20:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,淡出的时间算得正好\NThat was perfectly timed with his exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是不是先跟护士排练过\NDo you think he rehearsed that with the nurses beforehand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Max 好消息是\NYou know,Max,the good news is that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们知道 你能够自己改善自己的生活\Nnow we know you have the ability to improve your life all... by... yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧\NYeah,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.09,0:20:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很乐意帮你\NAnd I would be more than happy to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为 只要你下定决心\NBecause if you put your mind to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能做到原本只能梦想的事\Nyou could achieve things you only dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你意下如何\NSo what do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.95,0:20:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听起来好费劲 绝对没兴趣\NIt sounds like a lot of work. Hard pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我能理解\NYeah,that's okay. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.44,0:20:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我得走了 保重 - 再见 各位\N- Well,I gotta go,buddy. Take care. - Bye,everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我升职又失败了\NI got passed up for another promotion at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.78,0:20:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的需要改变一下\NI really need to change some things in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再想想 我干嘛要怀疑自己呢\NYou know,on second thought, why should I even doubt myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就不想要那个位子\NI mean,I don't even want that job anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.09,0:21:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 是\NYeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alex 你今天要跟Dave去看海豚么\NSo,Alex,are you going to that dolphin thing with Dave today?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕\NOh,no.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以的 我可以的\NI can do this. I can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.58,0:21:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 没门\NOh,no. No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.56,0:21:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你们想要什么\NI know what you guys want,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.56,0:21:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不会得逞的\Nand you're not gettin' it!
